"""
    Check that setting `data` to 'cps' uses cps data
    """
baseline = False
start_year = 2016
reform = {'II_em': {(2017): 10000}}
calc = get_micro_data.get_calculator(baseline, start_year, reform=reform,
    records_start_year=CPS_START_YEAR, data='cps')
assert calc.array('blind_head').sum() > 0 and calc.array('e00700').sum() == 0
